uration file describing the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"source’s contents and other metadata.","type":"text"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An initialized raster tile source."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"After initializing and configuring the source, add it to a map view’s style","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"using the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/addSource:","isActive":true},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The URL may be a full HTTP or HTTPS URL or canonical URL. The URL should","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"point to a JSON file that conforms to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"TileJSON specification","type":"text"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If a Mapbox URL is specified, this source uses a tile size of 256. For all","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"other tilesets, the default value is 512. (See the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTileSourceOptionTileSize","type":"reference"},{"text":" documentation for more information about tile","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sizes.) If you need to use a tile size other than the default, use the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"-initWithIdentifier:configurationURL:tileSize:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterTileSource\/ini